{"tid":934620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回應孟晚舟被捕　葉劉淑儀：將改用華為手機","createTime":"2018-12-09T11:55:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T02:57:10.000Z","uid":79563,"like":347,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"db605647548931f5aa7fb111eb84a9fa2375959c","tid":934620,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T11:55:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1432446_1_L_20181209190913.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1432446_1_L_20181209190913.jpg&h=79560f9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n華為集團副董事長孟晚舟日前在加拿大轉機時被捕。新民黨立法會議員葉劉淑儀表示，不會因此呼籲香港市民多用國貨，但自己會改用華為手機。她又說，華為的手機出口已超越蘋果公司，又正在5G流動通訊網絡市場上爭取領導地位，明白華為高層的一舉一動，受美國政府高度關注。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會立法會議員陸頌雄則呼籲，市民應多買國產品牌，以示對國家發展的支持，被問到會否呼籲工聯會會員不用蘋果產品iPhone，他說，在全球化社會下，要求市民罷買特定國家的產品有難度，亦應提倡公平貿易。"},{"pid":"75a55dd85db637bda9402e49a097cbce92f690f3","tid":934620,"uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T11:56:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd14e7429bcf758cc910ff82be30befd71779b8e","tid":934620,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T11:58:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe6182e529ed4624cf090ac7e1c368e2dce8b66","tid":934620,"uid":56881,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T12:00:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ea6ba917d22b4c9bf829c89b1fb40c18875583","tid":934620,"uid":62599,"like":128,"dislike":2,"score":126,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T12:00:10.000Z","msg":"正一癡撚咗線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/h